primary.context: Caller wants to make a payment for their timeshare maintenance fees
primary.detail: The agent verified the caller's identity and confirmed sending a payment link via email and text.

steps: Agent clarified the request for maintenance fees after a transcription error.
Agent performed account lookup via caller ID.
Agent verified caller name and state.
Agent confirmed contact information on file.
Agent initiated sending the payment link and closed the call.

clarifications.note: Transcription error 'mayonnaise and cheese' for maintenance fees

actions.detail: Found record matching caller's phone number
Sent maintenance fee link via email and text

insights.summary: The customer called to pay maintenance fees. The agent successfully verified the account and sent a payment link via text and email.
